the way they talk to you,

00:00:45.145 --> 00:00:46.746 line:5%,start
I think it's awful.

00:00:46.813 --> 00:00:50.650 line:5%,start
When those women say bad things
about you, it hurts my heart.

00:00:50.717 --> 00:00:52.452 line:5%,start
