and I think I did.

00:02:34.087 --> 00:02:36.389 line:95%,end
Next, Mackenzie.

00:02:36.456 --> 00:02:40.126 line:95%,end
Mackenzie, your routine
was a winning number.

00:02:40.193 --> 00:02:42.095 line:95%,end
