I don't do 10.

00:02:43.596 --> 00:02:45.899 line:95%,end
Next, Paige.

00:02:46.432 --> 00:02:47.567 line:95%,end
You went out there.

00:02:47.634 --> 00:02:49.169 line:95%,end
