00:02:51.204 --> 00:02:52.705 line:95%,end
Brooke.

00:02:52.772 --> 00:02:56.209 line:95%,end
Brooke, you're here because
you give me this much.

00:02:56.743 --> 00:02:59.812 line:95%,end
I don't see this effervescent personality.

00:02:59.879 --> 00:03:01.581 line:95%,end
You see this fake little smile.

00:03:01.981 --> 00:03:05.151 line:95%,end
You're concentrating so much
to not screw up the dance.

00:03:05.218 --> 00:03:07.320 line:95%,end
You can't have fun out there.

00:03:07.387 --> 00:03:09.122 line:95%,end
Next, I have Nia.

00:03:09.923 --> 00:03:11.324 line:95%,end
Nia, again, you're here

00:03:11.391 --> 00:03:13.826 line:95%,end
because you showed responsibility.

00:03:14.427 --> 00:03:15.461 line:95%,end
You quit fooling around.

00:03:15.528 --> 00:03:17.830 line:95%,end
And I didn't have to hear
your mouth all day long.

00:03:17.897 --> 00:03:18.898 line:95%,end
Yes?

00:03:19.599 --> 00:03:21.768 line:95%,end
And on top of the pyramid,
again, is Chloe.

00:03:22.368 --> 00:03:23.636 line:95%,end
