the last time we were in Chicago,

00:03:42.622 --> 00:03:43.456 line:95%,end
but we didn't win.

00:03:44.524 --> 00:03:45.858 line:95%,end
I'd like to win.

00:03:45.925 --> 00:03:50.496 line:95%,end
Nia, you and Mackenzie
will be doing a duet.

00:03:50.563 --> 00:03:52.632 line:95%,end
(clapping)

00:03:52.699 --> 00:03:54.400 line:95%,end
Paige, you have a solo.

00:03:55.301 --> 00:03:56.669 line:95%,end
