00:03:57.237 --> 00:03:59.772 line:95%,end
You can screw up your own dance
by missing the choreography,

00:03:59.839 --> 00:04:00.974 line:95%,end
but you can't mess up other people.

00:04:01.941 --> 00:04:04.377 line:95%,end
Brooke, you also have a solo.

00:04:04.777 --> 00:04:09.215 line:95%,end
Chloe, your solo is called "Unchained."

00:04:09.282 --> 00:04:11.451 line:95%,end
But you know what the rule is--

00:04:11.517 --> 00:04:13.987 line:95%,end
you're not in class, no solo.

00:04:14.053 --> 00:04:16.122 line:95%,end
So we need to figure out
what went on last night.

00:04:16.189 --> 00:04:18.558 line:95%,end
I had three faculty members
come and tell me,

00:04:18.625 --> 00:04:19.759 line:95%,end
where's Chloe?

00:04:19.826 --> 00:04:20.994 line:95%,end
Why isn't Chloe in class?

00:04:21.060 --> 00:04:22.195 line:95%,end
She was at the doctor.

00:04:22.262 --> 00:04:24.330 line:95%,end
But you need to have some
type of common courtesy

00:04:24.397 --> 00:04:25.865 line:95%,end
or at least say,

00:04:25.932 --> 00:04:27.467 line:95%,end
"Hey, I'm taking my kid to the doctor.

00:04:27.533 --> 00:04:28.868 line:95%,end
I'll bring a doctor's excuse."

00:04:28.935 --> 00:04:29.836 line:95%,end
I have one.

00:04:29.902 --> 00:04:31.304 line:95%,end
ABBY: Good.

00:04:31.371 --> 00:04:33.740 line:95%,end
Now girls, I look at this pyramid

00:04:33.806 --> 00:04:35.341 line:95%,end
and I don't even want to do a group dance

00:04:35.408 --> 00:04:36.576 line:95%,end
because you're lazy.

00:04:36.643 --> 00:04:37.477 line:95%,end
You're lifeless.

00:04:37.543 --> 00:04:39.112 line:95%,end
And you don't give me 150%.

00:04:39.178 --> 00:04:43.216 line:95%,end
Now this routine is about zombies

00:04:43.283 --> 00:04:45.184 line:95%,end
