00:04:50.256 --> 00:04:52.191 line:95%,end
Holly, you're not working anymore.

00:04:52.258 --> 00:04:53.960 line:95%,end
You've all the time in the world.

00:04:54.027 --> 00:04:57.230 line:95%,end
So you are in charge of the costumes.


00:04:57.297 --> 00:04:58.264 line:95%,end
For the group number?

00:04:58.331 --> 00:04:59.666 line:95%,end
ABBY: Yes.

00:04:59.732 --> 00:05:01.567 line:5%,start
I am not looking forward
to creating the costumes

00:05:01.634 --> 00:05:03.436 line:5%,start
