00:05:05.638 --> 00:05:07.473 line:95%,end
All right. Moms, you're dismissed.

00:05:07.540 --> 00:05:09.642 line:95%,end
Holly, don't procrastinate.

00:05:09.709 --> 00:05:11.411 line:95%,end
Everybody else spread apart.

00:05:11.477 --> 00:05:15.715 line:95%,end
(upbeat music playing)

00:05:19.886 --> 00:05:23.523 line:5%,start
