and wiggle your head back.

00:05:23.589 --> 00:05:24.590 line:5%,start
(makes noises)

00:05:24.657 --> 00:05:26.993 line:5%,start
<i>This week, the number called "Glam"</i>

00:05:27.060 --> 00:05:28.227 line:95%,end
is all about zombies.

00:05:28.294 --> 00:05:30.463 line:95%,end
<i>And after last week's travesty,</i>

00:05:30.530 --> 00:05:32.732 line:95%,end
<i>I really need these girls</i>
<i>to get it together.</i>

00:05:32.799 --> 00:05:33.866 line:95%,end
<i>I need to win.</i>

00:05:33.933 --> 00:05:36.636 line:95%,end
The kids are busts on a statue.

00:05:36.703 --> 00:05:38.771 line:95%,end
So it's like you have the long column,

00:05:38.838 --> 00:05:40.640 line:95%,end
and then you have their head
sitting on top of it.

00:05:40.707 --> 00:05:42.508 line:95%,end
<i>It's a very cool effect.</i>

00:05:42.575 --> 00:05:43.810 line:95%,end
I hope the judges get it.

00:05:44.577 --> 00:05:46.646 line:95%,end
Make sure you hit that
back attitude, Paige.

00:05:46.713 --> 00:05:48.047 line:95%,end
SINGER:
<i>âª Go, go, go, go âª</i>

