00:06:15.508 --> 00:06:16.342 line:95%,end
(chuckles)
I know.

00:06:16.409 --> 00:06:18.411 line:95%,end
And you know, you're not
getting along with Abby

00:06:18.478 --> 00:06:19.545 line:95%,end
the best right now.

00:06:19.612 --> 00:06:21.647 line:95%,end
Do you think that's why
she's at bottom of the pyramid?

00:06:21.714 --> 00:06:23.816 line:95%,end
No. Everything's fine.

00:06:23.883 --> 00:06:25.685 line:95%,end
I mean, it's never going to be what it was

00:06:25.752 --> 00:06:27.186 line:95%,end
because she doesn't need me anymore.

00:06:27.253 --> 00:06:29.789 line:95%,end
