care of all of her business.

00:06:29.856 --> 00:06:33.326 line:95%,end
I'm not working at the front desk
anymore actually for Abby

00:06:33.393 --> 00:06:35.895 line:95%,end
because we did find someone
to replace me.

00:06:35.962 --> 00:06:37.797 line:95%,end
And I really don't have the time.

00:06:37.864 --> 00:06:40.933 line:95%,end
I miss it terribly,
and the people miss me.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:43.002 line:95%,end
I get emails every day from people.

00:06:43.069 --> 00:06:44.570 line:95%,end
But I just don't have the time.

00:06:44.637 --> 00:06:46.973 line:95%,end
I don't think it has anything to do
with me, to be honest with you.

00:06:47.039 --> 00:06:48.007 line:95%,end
See, I don't agree with that.

00:06:48.074 --> 00:06:49.742 line:95%,end
-I really don't.
-MELISSA: You don't?

00:06:49.809 --> 00:06:52.979 line:95%,end
The reason she's at the bottom
is because you didn't kiss her ass

00:06:53.045 --> 00:06:54.847 line:95%,end
and do everything she wanted
you to do last week.

00:06:54.914 --> 00:06:57.450 line:95%,end
I'm getting so much slack from everybody

00:06:57.517 --> 00:06:59.619 line:95%,end
that, you know, I always kiss
your butt and everything.

00:06:59.685 --> 00:07:00.787 line:95%,end
So what's the issue?

00:07:00.853 --> 00:07:01.754 line:95%,end
-I don't think (indistinct)
-I think you need

00:07:01.821 --> 00:07:02.855 line:95%,end
to confront her more.

00:07:02.922 --> 00:07:05.391 line:95%,end
<i>I think Melissa has retired</i>
<i>from her duties</i>

00:07:05.458 --> 00:07:08.494 line:5%,start
