she's made it quite clear

00:07:08.561 --> 00:07:09.996 line:5%,start
that she doesn't need to work anymore.

00:07:10.062 --> 00:07:12.365 line:95%,end
And I think that has caused a rift
between her and Abby

00:07:12.432 --> 00:07:15.101 line:95%,end
because Abby's used to Melissa
being at her beck and call.

00:07:15.168 --> 00:07:16.269 line:95%,end
Stand up for yourself.

00:07:17.837 --> 00:07:20.840 line:5%,start
(upbeat music playing)

00:07:22.308 --> 00:07:24.277 line:95%,end
ABBY: Stop.
I gave that whole speech--

00:07:24.677 --> 00:07:26.012 line:95%,end
big! Big!

00:07:26.078 --> 00:07:28.714 line:95%,end
Paige is doing a solo this week, finally.

00:07:28.781 --> 00:07:30.183 line:95%,end
<i>She is doing "Tongue Twister."</i>

00:07:30.249 --> 00:07:33.419 line:95%,end
<i>Now this is a number</i>
<i>that she did a year ago.</i>

00:07:33.486 --> 00:07:35.988 line:95%,end
