00:07:36.055 --> 00:07:37.690 line:95%,end
and she never did it on stage.

00:07:37.757 --> 00:07:39.225 line:95%,end
Face!

00:07:39.292 --> 00:07:40.827 line:95%,end
You have the face. Use it.

00:07:41.928 --> 00:07:44.096 line:95%,end
This week, my solo has
a little bit of everything--

00:07:44.163 --> 00:07:46.466 line:95%,end
<i>jazz, acro, gymnastics.</i>

00:07:46.532 --> 00:07:48.067 line:95%,end
I like this solo a lot.

00:07:48.134 --> 00:07:49.535 line:95%,end
Right. Get over there in the corner.

00:07:49.602 --> 00:07:52.472 line:95%,end
Remember, you either make a fool
out of yourself or you win.

00:07:52.538 --> 00:07:53.873 line:95%,end
The option is up to you.

00:07:53.940 --> 00:07:54.774 line:95%,end
