00:07:56.108 --> 00:07:57.109 line:95%,end
Brooke, let's see it.

00:07:57.176 --> 00:08:00.513 line:5%,start
(dance music playing)

00:08:00.580 --> 00:08:01.981 line:5%,start
Oh, right there.
Get in your feet.

00:08:02.048 --> 00:08:03.616 line:95%,end
Get off your heels.

00:08:03.683 --> 00:08:07.086 line:95%,end
Brooke has her work cut
out for her this week.

00:08:07.153 --> 00:08:09.755 line:95%,end
<i>This solo is tough.</i>

00:08:09.822 --> 00:08:12.191 line:95%,end
<i>Her routine is called</i>
<i>"Paint the Picture"</i>

00:08:12.258 --> 00:08:15.394 line:95%,end
because she actually makes
pictures with her body.

00:08:15.461 --> 00:08:18.464 line:95%,end
<i>She has one trick after</i>
<i>another after another.</i>

00:08:18.531 --> 00:08:20.566 line:95%,end
<i>So her stamina needs to be built up.</i>

00:08:20.633 --> 00:08:22.935 line:95%,end
And she has to knock
one out of the park.

00:08:23.002 --> 00:08:26.339 line:95%,end
You're dismissed.
Have your mother meet me outside, pronto.

00:08:30.710 --> 00:08:32.645 line:95%,end
I want to talk to you--a couple things.

00:08:32.712 --> 00:08:35.147 line:95%,end
-Okay.
-First of all, Paige has a prop.

00:08:35.214 --> 00:08:36.182 line:95%,end
She has the chair.

00:08:36.549 --> 00:08:39.452 line:95%,end
The chair needs some rubber
stoppers on the bottom of it

00:08:39.519 --> 00:08:41.487 line:95%,end
so that doesn't move
on her on stage.

00:08:41.554 --> 00:08:42.722 line:95%,end
-Okay.
-So I'm letting you

00:08:42.788 --> 00:08:44.323 line:95%,end
take that chair home tonight.

00:08:45.291 --> 00:08:46.826 line:95%,end
Get whatever you need done to it.

00:08:46.893 --> 00:08:49.195 line:95%,end
And make sure tomorrow,
she has it to practice with.

00:08:49.262 --> 00:08:50.897 line:95%,end
The other thing I want
to talk to you about

00:08:50.963 --> 00:08:53.199 line:95%,end
is Brooke and the voice lessons.

00:08:53.566 --> 00:08:56.168 line:95%,end
I want her to take from the woman
that teaches here.

00:08:56.235 --> 00:08:58.638 line:95%,end
I don't care what you've heard.
I don't care if you like her or not.

00:08:58.704 --> 00:09:00.339 line:95%,end
<i>Brooke wants to sing.</i>

00:09:00.406 --> 00:09:02.074 line:95%,end
